// KioskAlbumGrid — lightweight wrapping grid of KioskCards for the kiosk
// Search/Library album tabs (2.0.2 frente #3). Absolute-positioned cells inside
// a vertical Flickable; card width derives from the grid width so it reflows.
//
// WINDOWED (in-window pattern, mirrors the desktop Carousel): the `for` creates
// only cheap empty positioned slots for every album, but the heavy KioskCard
// (Image + text) mounts ONLY for slots whose band intersects the viewport. A
// plain full grid mounted every card at once and spiked CPU on entry — a Pi
// can't afford that. Binds `[AlbumCardItem]` so artwork pushes land on the cards.
import { Theme } from "../foundation/semantic-colors.slint";
import { AlbumCardItem } from "../state.slint";
import { KioskCard } from "KioskCard.slint";

export component KioskAlbumGrid inherits Flickable {
    in property <[AlbumCardItem]> albums;
    in property <int> columns: 6;
    in property <length> gap: 16px;
    in property <length> pad: 16px;
    callback open(string);

    property <length> card-w: (self.width - 2 * root.pad - (root.columns - 1) * root.gap) / root.columns;
    property <length> card-h: root.card-w + 46px;
    property <float> rows: Math.ceil(root.albums.length / root.columns);

    viewport-width: self.width;
    viewport-height: root.rows * (root.card-h + root.gap) + root.pad;

    Rectangle {
        for album[i] in root.albums: slot := Rectangle {
            x: root.pad + Math.mod(i, root.columns) * (root.card-w + root.gap);
            y: root.pad + Math.floor(i / root.columns) * (root.card-h + root.gap);
            width: root.card-w;
            height: root.card-h;
            // Visible band (content coords) is [-viewport-y, -viewport-y+height];
            // 240px margin keeps a card mounted just off-screen for smooth scroll.
            property <bool> in-window: (self.y + self.height >= -root.viewport-y - 240px)
                && (self.y <= -root.viewport-y + root.height + 240px);
            if slot.in-window: KioskCard {
                width: root.card-w;
                art-size: root.card-w;
                album: album;
                clicked(id) => {
                    root.open(id);
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
